title: iPexpert's Cisco CCIE RS (v5) Lab VoD :: Next Generation
description:
iPexpert's Cisco CCIE R&S (v5) Lab VoD :: Next Generation
-----------------------------------------------------------


During this high-definition, studio-recorded video course, you'll instantly be engaged as you watch Marko Milivojevic (CCIE x2 :: R&S and SP) and Terry Vinson (CCIE x2 :: R&S and Data Center), two of the industry's most respected instructors, explain the theory, conduct white boarding and configure countless advanced, technology-focused lab scenarios on nearly every protocol or technology that you'll encounter on the actual CCIE R&S V5 lab exam.

As you begin your CCIE lab preparation, it's important to understand the protocols and technologies listed in the CCIE blueprint in mastery detail. iPexpert's CCIE R&S V5 Lab VoD was designed to do that. The quality and amount of content covered (Over 150 hours), as well as the quality of the delivery and presentation of this one-of-a-kind video class, makes for a training resource that's unmatched within the Cisco training industry
